snippet.title: Gravity Falls: Legend of the Gnome Gemulets - Launch Trailer [North America]
snippet.description:
Only YOU can solve the mystery of Gravity Falls, exclusively on Nintendo 3DS! Explore the town and solve an all-new mystery, using magical weapons to beat monsters! 

Learn more here: https://www.ubisoft.com/en-US/game/gravity-falls/

© Disney
